high_descs: Turn left and move to the large sofa on your right.
Pick up the remote on the left.
Turn around, move towards the TV, and turn left towards the coffee table.
Place the remote on to the coffee table.
Turn to the left and walk around the room, stopping behind the large sofa.
Pick up the remote from the sofa.
Turn to the right and walk around the room towards the television, stopping in front of the coffee table.
Place the remote onto the middle of the coffee table
anns.task_desc: Pick up the remote controls off the sofa and place them on the coffee table.

high_descs: Turn around, go forward, turn right to face the couch.
Take the left remote control from the couch.
Turn around, go forward to the TV, turn left, go forward a step, turn left to face the coffee table.
Put the remote control on the coffee table near the bottom right corner of the statue.
Turn left, go forward, turn right before reaching the table, go forward past the couch, turn left, go forward, turn right to face the couch.
Take the remote control from the couch.
Turn right, go forward, turn left before reaching the table, go forward to the wall, turn left, go forward, turn left to face the coffee table.
Put the remote control behind the statue on the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Put two remote controls on a coffee table.
